data.description: Cute, one story ranch style home with large rocking chair front porch set on a large lot. Three bedrooms with two full baths. Open concept great room with vaulted ceiling and wood burning fireplace, includes dining area. Spacious primary bedroom with full bath. All stainless appliances in the kitchen. Oak cabinets. New oak flooring in great room and dining area. Small four-season room located off dining area that would make a great office or craft space with separate entry.  Laundry closet in hallway. Detached storage shed.
